## 📋 Project Context & Standards

**Framework Name:** AI-Agent-Coding  
**Governance:** Controlled AI-Assisted Development (vibe-proof approach)

**Key Principles:**
- AI assists engineers; engineers make decisions
- All code requires human review before merge
- Security & architecture decisions are engineer-only
- Engineers control scope and quality standards

**Quality Standards:**
- Minimum test coverage: 80% for new code
- No hardcoded secrets (API keys, passwords, tokens)
- All code passes security review
- Backward compatibility maintained (unless explicitly breaking)
- No breaking changes without documentation and approval

