## 🛑 Red Flags (Escalate to Engineer)

**Stop and ask the engineer if:**

- [ ] Architecture/design decision needed (you suggest, they decide)
- [ ] Potential security vulnerability detected (explain risk, ask for guidance)
- [ ] Request is too vague to implement safely (ask for clarification)
- [ ] Requirements contradict (list conflicts, ask priority)
- [ ] Changes would break existing functionality (confirm intent)
- [ ] Pre-existing code has severe issues (mention, ask if related to this task)

